				<li id="16738725" class="cmnt-root" data="14" data-d="1658115436000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><div class="comment-username">Anonymous</div></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t578140/Halberd" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">17 Jul 2022 23:37</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16738725" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">This is a humble weapon, but let that not deceive you. It is a most excellent all-rounder of a weapon, with the light attacks being reliable thrusts without good speed, reach, pacing, and tracking. The strong attacks are wide sweeps, allowing one to inflict good damage against multiple targets. The guard counter is a little on the slow side, but carries with it a high amount of stagger and damage.<br/><br/>The default skill ought to be changed when possible, as the running light is a good alternative. Personally, I think War Cry is a good shout (pun intended), as it boosts attack by about 10%, buy alters the strong attacks, giving you hyper armour and better range. You can take advantage of certain talismans like the Axe Talisman for increased damage on charged attacks, and the Roar Medallion for increased damage using shout attacks, both of which War Cry benefit from.<br/><br/>In short, this is a very good weapon, and is extremely reliable. It is the Nissan Skyline R34 holding its own against the Ferraris and Lamborghinis of Elden Ring; a surprising beast with a simple look that offers a beautiful dirge of death as it keeps up with heavyweight superstars.</p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16738725" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16738725" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">0</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>15</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>1</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16738725"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16738725" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16738725"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
